{"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier for the current device.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"userId"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates a unique user ID with the device to:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Track users across multiple devices"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable user-based targeting in campaigns"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link push engagement to user accounts in your analytics"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Support user migration between devices","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Set user ID after successful login:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class AuthenticationService {","","    func handleSuccessfulLogin(user: User) {","        \/\/ Set user ID for cross-device tracking","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","","        \/\/ Set email if available","        if let email = user.email {","            Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","        }","","        \/\/ Update user profile tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"logged_in\": true,","            \"login_date\": Date(),","            \"login_count\": incrementLoginCount(),","            \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"subscription_status\": user.subscription?.status.rawValue ?? \"none\"","        ])","","        \/\/ Sync with analytics platforms","        Analytics.identify(user.id, traits: [","            \"email\": user.email ?? \"\",","            \"pushwoosh_hwid\": Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","        ])","","        Logger.info(\"User logged in: \\(user.id)\")","    }","","    func handleAccountDeletion() {","        \/\/ Clear user identity","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(\"\")","","        \/\/ Clear all user data tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"logged_in\": false,","            \"user_id\": NSNull(),","            \"email\": NSNull(),","            \"account_deleted\": true,","            \"deletion_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Unregister from push","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { _ in }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setUserId:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"}],"title":"setUserId:","modules":[{"name":